## 三、高频固定短语 & 搭配

> 听力 Section A + 阅读 + 写作通用

| 短语 | 释义 | 高频场景 | 例句 |
|------|------|----------|------|
| **a variety of** | 种种；多种多样 | 阅读/写作，表列举 | *The robot can adapt to a variety of complex scenarios.* |
| **take place** | 发生；举行 | ⭐ 听力新闻超高频 | *The national robot competition will take place next month.* |
| **curled up** | 卷着的；蜷缩 | 阅读叙事场景 | — |
| **bring together** | 聚集；召集；整合 | 写作/听力，表整合资源 | *This project brings together mechanical engineering and artificial intelligence technology.* |
| **inspire sb. to do sth.** | 激励 / 启发某人做某事 | 写作/阅读，固定搭配 | *This open source project inspired me to learn more about robotics.* |

